      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Fearsome Apex Rathalos",
        "Client": "Felyne with a Singed Tail",
        "Description": "Talk about a bad fur day! Just when\r\nmy tail healed up, I come across\r\nan even meaner Rathalos! An Apex\r\none, too! As soon as it spotted me\r\nit barfed up this meowssive fireball!\r\nAt this point, the fur on my tail will\r\nnever grow back...",
        "Target": "Hunt an Apex Rathalos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Redout\u00E9 Rathalos sup\u00E9rieur",
        "Client": "Felyne \u00E0 queue br\u00FBl\u00E9e",
        "Description": "J\u0027ai vraiment pas de chance,\r\nchapristi ! Ma queue avait enfin\r\ngu\u00E9ri, et voil\u00E0 qu\u0027un Rathalos\r\nsup\u00E9rieur me tombe dessus ! D\u00E8s\r\nqu\u0027il m\u0027a vu, il m\u0027a balanc\u00E9 une\r\n\u00E9norme boule de feu ! Ma\r\nfourrure s\u0027en remettra jamais...",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rathalos sup\u00E9rieur",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il temibile Rathalos Apex",
        "Client": "Felyne dalla coda bruciata",
        "Description": "Che brutta giornata per il mio\r\npelo! Proprio quando la mia\r\ncoda era guarita, mi sono\r\nimbattuto in un Rathalos. Per\r\ngiunta un Apex! Vedendomi, ha\r\nsputato una palla di fuoco. Il\r\npelo non ricrescer\u00E0 pi\u00F9...",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rathalos Apex",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Der furchtbare Apex-Rathalos",
        "Client": "Leicht angesengter Felyne",
        "Description": "Was f\u00FCr eine Katzastrophe f\u00FCr mein\r\nFell! Mein Schwanz ist grad verheilt,\r\nda treff ich auf einen noch fieseren\r\nRathalos! Ein Apex auch noch! Kaum\r\nhatte er mich gesehen, spie er schon\r\neinen riesigen Feuerball! So w\u00E4chst\r\nmein Schwanzfell nie nach...",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Apex-Rathalos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "El temible Rathalos Apex",
        "Client": "Felyne de cola chamuscada",
        "Description": "\u00A1Qu\u00E9 mala racha con mi pelo!\r\nAhora que se me hab\u00EDa curado\r\nla cola, un Rathalos va y me\r\nla quema de nuevo. \u00BFSabes qu\u00E9?\r\n\u00A1Me da igual si es un Apex!\r\n\u00A1Voy a ir y... pedirle a\r\nalguien que lo cace!",
        "Target": "Caza un Rathalos Apex",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0416\u0443\u0442\u043A\u0438\u0439 \u0432\u044B\u0441\u0448\u0438\u0439 \u0420\u0430\u0442\u0430\u043B\u043E\u0441",
